WEBVTT

00:01:01.030 --> 00:01:03.100
Trisha Prabhu: My parents
are from India.

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:05.610
But I was born in America.

00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:08.840
I was born and brought up there
and am studying there.

00:01:09.750 --> 00:01:12.180
I was just 13

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:18.280
when I read about a young girl
named Rebecca who had committed suicide.

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:21.240
She was just 12 years old at that time.

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:25.410
Younger than me,
when she took her own life.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.000
The reason?

00:01:27.050 --> 00:01:28.950
Repeated cyber bullying.

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:31.860
In the cyber world and social media,